sprykerComponent.name: active-filter-price-range
sprykerComponent.readme:
Displays a selected filter, which shows a price range.

Code sample

{% include molecule('active-filter-price-range', 'CatalogPage') with {
     data: {
         filter: filter,
         min: min,
         activeMin: activeMin,
         max: max,
         activeMax: activeMax
     }
 } only %}

defines.name: data
defines.contract:
filter: required,
    min: required,
    activeMin: required,
    max: required,
    activeMax: required
